<h1>How to Run JavaScript</h1>
    
    <p>There are two main ways you will be integrating JavaScript into your HTML code:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Using the <code>&ltscript&gt</code> tag</li>
      <li>Using an external file</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>This is very similar to CSS, as you can use the <code>&ltstyle&gt</code> tag</li> or link an external CSS file. </p>

